    <name>Smiles</name>
    <summary>Meme gallery with tagging</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Smiles allows you to tag your memes for finding them quickly when necessary, optionally also working as a URL launcher</p>
        <p>Some features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Hover to play a video, or right-click it to play</li>
          <li>Hover to unmute videos</li>
          <li>Tagging and hiding individual files</li>
          <li>Add a URL to launch when clicking</li>
          <li>File color themeing</li>
          <li>Drop to add files</li>
          <li>Drag files from inside the app to other apps (such as uploads)</li>
          <li>Sorting by random, alphabetical order, or date order</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <branding>
        <color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#f6d32d</color>
